ould ",["swear by",["study-note-ref","a",["GR promise, confirm by an oath."]]]," no greater, he ",["sware",["study-note-ref","b",[["Jer. 44:26","ot/jer/44.26"],"; ",["Amos 6:8","ot/amos/6.8"],"."]]]," by himself,"]],[14,["Saying, Surely blessing I will ",["bless",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Abrahamic Covenant","tg/abrahamic-covenant"],"."]]]," thee, and multiplying I will multiply thee."]],[15,["And so, after he had patiently ",["endured",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Perseverance","tg/perseverance"],"."]]],", he obtained the promise."]],[16,["For men verily swear by the greater: and an ",["oath",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Oath","tg/oath"],"."]]]," for confirmation ",["is",["clarity-word"]]," to them an end of all ",["strife",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Strife","tg/strife"],"."]]],"."]],[17,["Wherein God, willing more abundantly to shew unto the heirs of promise the immutability of his ",["counsel",["study-note-ref","a",["GR design, purpose. ",["TG Counselor","tg/counselor"],"."]]],", ",["confirmed",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Vow","tg/vow"],"."]]]," ",["it",["clarity-word"]]," by an ",["oath",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Covenants","tg/covenants"],"."]]],":"]],[18,["That by two immutable things, in which ",["it was",["clarity-word"]]," impossible for God to ",["lie",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG God, Perfection of","tg/god-perfection-of"],"."]]],", we might have a strong consolation, who have fled for ",["refuge",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Refuge","tg/refuge"],"."]]]," to lay hold upon the ",["hope",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Hope","tg/hope"],"."]]]," set before us:"]],[19,["Which ",["hope",["clarity-word"]]," we have as an ",["anchor",["study-note-ref","a",[["Ether 12:4","bofm/ether/12.4"],"."]]]," of the soul, both sure and steadfast, and which entereth into that within the ",["veil",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Veil","tg/veil"],"."]]],";"]],[20,["Whither the forerunner is for us entered, ",["even",["clarity-word"]]," Jesus, made an ",["high priest",["study-note-ref